description: Support to the High-level International Conference on the Mid-Term Comprehensive Review of the Implementation of the International Decade for Action, “Water for Life” 2005-2015

subproject.description: The project goal is to render support to the Government of the Republic of Tajikistan in organizing and conducting the International Conference, that will bring together representatives of international community, governmental institutions and non-governmental organizations, civil society and private sector to discuss the implementation of International Decade of Actions “Water for Life” 2005-2015.
